# Normalize line endings: store and check out text files as LF on every
# platform. This overrides a local core.autocrlf=true, which otherwise rewrites
# the working tree to CRLF and produces phantom EOL-only diffs whenever a
# formatter (ruff, prettier) writes a file with LF.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Common binary types — never normalize, never diff as text.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
